ANGRY residents of Umlazi E section south of Durban allegedly took the law into their own hands. According to witnesses, police had taken a suspect, Wiseman Nguse (40) to his home in the area allegedly to verify his residential address. He was accompanied by two officers from Bayview Police Station. if(typeof za24_DisplayAd != "undefined") za24_DisplayAd("300x250","2");var viewReq = new Array();function vu(u) {var i=new Image();i.src=u.replace("&amp;","&");viewReq.push(i);}vu("https://securepubads.g.doubleclick.net/pcs/view?xai\x3dAKAOjstuGsGRhLKnlxBKkoYvupDm6IRzUQ3bVY5WQxJov9HtlTlTfCKq4RPh1UDJAkNZ-LKtCv0676P7Y6V9ERXT1LHagpwZAE94egCVzrGz-JM4SDJfIkog0B4vNEbT2EHKXLhvJmFm7AUIf_6sHcZyCmX3l2WwTwRiWMxX591YNlyhPhIdBQxkwcOUU-Ycbs6I28OMxUSZIvAJVnQLTqCkjBrgJnpYYOth23PN_KZXhb2ElfwXuKz4nXJWIKrHHWRy1BvbSHzzYCVMm5yxpDQh84G2jb2c_8w\x26sig\x3dCg0ArKJSzOtQDg9VbQJNEAE\x26urlfix\x3d1\x26adurl\x3d")

   
